children.text: The diagonal speedbracing has not been properly fixed to the cut-off roof trusses.
The relevant Australian Standard, AS 4440 Installation of Nail-Plated Timber Roof Trusses, clause 4.3.8 Fixing, provides a detail outlining the method for properly bracing cut-off trusses;
Diagonal speedbracing must be installed to these cut-off trusses in accordance with Australian Standard AS 4440, to ensure the performance of the roof bracing system.
